### ==========================================
### 🔐 AUTH ENDPOINTS
### ==========================================

### Register — Client
POST http://localhost:6868/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "firstName": "Karthik",
    "lastName": "Engili",
    "email": "karthik@test.com",
    "password": "test1234",
    "role": "CLIENT"
}

###

### Register — Freelancer
POST http://localhost:6868/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "firstName": "Alex",
    "lastName": "Dev",
    "email": "alex@test.com",
    "password": "test1234",
    "role": "FREELANCER"
}

###

### Register — Second Freelancer
POST http://localhost:6868/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "firstName": "Sara",
    "lastName": "Code",
    "email": "sara@test.com",
    "password": "test1234",
    "role": "FREELANCER"
