###

### Login — Client
POST http://localhost:6868/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "karthik@test.com",
    "password": "test1234"
}

###

### Login — Freelancer
POST http://localhost:6868/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "alex@test.com",
    "password": "test1234"
}

###

### Login — Second Freelancer
POST http://localhost:6868/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "sara@test.com",
    "password": "test1234"
}

###

### Logout
POST http://localhost:6868/api/auth/logout

###

### Get Current User (must be logged in)
GET http://localhost:6868/api/auth/me

